p: In the District Court holding Terms at Montesano

The Territory of Washington vs. Gus Beudjus Robert Stroughlaud Pete Peterson Ben Fredrickson Frank Nelson Fred Strombuger John Blending Andrew Johnson Leander Brown John Saxon John Thompson Alex Agreu Thomas Jacobs E. Envee Andrew Anderson Charles Burke } Warrant
The President of the United States To the Sheriff of Chehalis County Greeting:

Whereas, Gus Beudjus, Robert Struogland,
Pete Peterson, Ben Fredrickson, Frank Nelson, Fred Stromberger, John Bleuding, Andrew Johnson, Leander Brown, John Saxon, John Tompson, Alex Agreu, Thomas Jacobs, E. Emil, Andrew Anderson, Charles Burke having been duly indicted in the District Court of the Second Judicial District of Washington Territory, holding Terms at Montesano of the crime of Malicious Mischeif all of which appears to be of record

Now this is to command you, the said Sheriff, to take the said Gus Beudjus, Robert Stronglaud, Pete Peterson, Ben Fredrickson, Frank Nelson, Fred Stromberger, John Bleuding, Andrew Johnson, Leander Brown, John Saxon, John Thompson, Alex Agreu, Thomas Jacobs, E. Emel, Andrew Anderson, Charles Burke and them the said Gus Beudjus, Robert Stronglaud, Pete Peterson, Ben Fredrickson, Frank Nelson, Fred Stromberger, John Bleuding, Andrew Johnson, Leander Brown, John Saxon, John Thompson, Alex Agreu, Thomas Jacobs, E. Emel, Andrew Anderson, Charles Burke safely keep and have them forthwith in this Court there to answer to said charge, and abide such further order as the Court may make in the premises Herein fail not
